---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import brandingHero from '../../public/branding-graphic.png';

---

<section class="exp-issues sc-pd">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="exp-issues-row fx fx-jb">
            <div class="exp-lcol">
                <h2>What This Expertise Solves</h2>
                <div class="sc-txt">
                    <p>A strong brand does more than look good — <br/> it removes friction, creates trust, and drives decisions. <br/> Businesses come to us when they struggle with:</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="exp-rcol fx fx-wrap">
                <div class="exp-iss-col fx fx-ae fx-wrap">
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-top fx">
                        <div class="exp-iss-icon">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="23" viewBox="0 0 24 23" fill="none">
                                <path d="M10.2679 2C11.0377 0.666667 12.9623 0.666667 13.7321 2L22.3923 17C23.1621 18.3333 22.1999 20 20.6603 20H3.33975C1.80015 20 0.837895 18.3333 1.6077 17L10.2679 2Z" stroke="#FF6725" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                <path d="M12 15C12.5523 15 13 15.4477 13 16C13 16.5523 12.5523 17 12 17C11.4477 17 11 16.5523 11 16C11 15.4477 11.4477 15 12 15ZM12 7C12.5523 7 13 7.44772 13 8V12C13 12.5523 12.5523 13 12 13C11.4477 13 11 12.5523 11 12V8C11 7.44772 11.4477 7 12 7Z" fill="#FF6725"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Lack of brand clarity</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-btm">
                        <div class="exp-txt">
                            <p>Your audience cannot understand who you are or why you matter.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="exp-iss-col fx fx-ae fx-wrap">
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-top fx">
                        <div class="exp-iss-icon">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="23" viewBox="0 0 24 23" fill="none">
                                <path d="M10.2679 2C11.0377 0.666667 12.9623 0.666667 13.7321 2L22.3923 17C23.1621 18.3333 22.1999 20 20.6603 20H3.33975C1.80015 20 0.837895 18.3333 1.6077 17L10.2679 2Z" stroke="#FF6725" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                <path d="M12 15C12.5523 15 13 15.4477 13 16C13 16.5523 12.5523 17 12 17C11.4477 17 11 16.5523 11 16C11 15.4477 11.4477 15 12 15ZM12 7C12.5523 7 13 7.44772 13 8V12C13 12.5523 12.5523 13 12 13C11.4477 13 11 12.5523 11 12V8C11 7.44772 11.4477 7 12 7Z" fill="#FF6725"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Inconsistent or outdated visual identity</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-btm">
                        <div class="exp-txt">
                            <p>Your brand feels mismatched, disconnected, or unprofessional.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="exp-iss-col fx fx-ae fx-wrap">
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-top fx">
                        <div class="exp-iss-icon">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="23" viewBox="0 0 24 23" fill="none">
                                <path d="M10.2679 2C11.0377 0.666667 12.9623 0.666667 13.7321 2L22.3923 17C23.1621 18.3333 22.1999 20 20.6603 20H3.33975C1.80015 20 0.837895 18.3333 1.6077 17L10.2679 2Z" stroke="#FF6725" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                <path d="M12 15C12.5523 15 13 15.4477 13 16C13 16.5523 12.5523 17 12 17C11.4477 17 11 16.5523 11 16C11 15.4477 11.4477 15 12 15ZM12 7C12.5523 7 13 7.44772 13 8V12C13 12.5523 12.5523 13 12 13C11.4477 13 11 12.5523 11 12V8C11 7.44772 11.4477 7 12 7Z" fill="#FF6725"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Difficulty standing out in a saturated market</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-btm">
                        <div class="exp-txt">
                            <p>Competitors blend together — your brand disappears in the noise.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="exp-iss-col fx fx-ae fx-wrap">
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-top fx">
                        <div class="exp-iss-icon">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="23" viewBox="0 0 24 23" fill="none">
                                <path d="M10.2679 2C11.0377 0.666667 12.9623 0.666667 13.7321 2L22.3923 17C23.1621 18.3333 22.1999 20 20.6603 20H3.33975C1.80015 20 0.837895 18.3333 1.6077 17L10.2679 2Z" stroke="#FF6725" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                <path d="M12 15C12.5523 15 13 15.4477 13 16C13 16.5523 12.5523 17 12 17C11.4477 17 11 16.5523 11 16C11 15.4477 11.4477 15 12 15ZM12 7C12.5523 7 13 7.44772 13 8V12C13 12.5523 12.5523 13 12 13C11.4477 13 11 12.5523 11 12V8C11 7.44772 11.4477 7 12 7Z" fill="#FF6725"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Low trust or low confidence in digital channels</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-btm">
                        <div class="exp-txt">
                            <p>Users hesitate to engage or convert because the brand lacks credibility.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="exp-iss-col fx fx-ae fx-wrap">
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-top fx">
                        <div class="exp-iss-icon">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="23" viewBox="0 0 24 23" fill="none">
                                <path d="M10.2679 2C11.0377 0.666667 12.9623 0.666667 13.7321 2L22.3923 17C23.1621 18.3333 22.1999 20 20.6603 20H3.33975C1.80015 20 0.837895 18.3333 1.6077 17L10.2679 2Z" stroke="#FF6725" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                <path d="M12 15C12.5523 15 13 15.4477 13 16C13 16.5523 12.5523 17 12 17C11.4477 17 11 16.5523 11 16C11 15.4477 11.4477 15 12 15ZM12 7C12.5523 7 13 7.44772 13 8V12C13 12.5523 12.5523 13 12 13C11.4477 13 11 12.5523 11 12V8C11 7.44772 11.4477 7 12 7Z" fill="#FF6725"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Internal confusion on messaging and positioning</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-btm">
                        <div class="exp-txt">
                            <p>Different departments say different things — creating misalignment.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="exp-iss-col fx fx-ae fx-wrap">
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-top fx">
                        <div class="exp-iss-icon">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="23" viewBox="0 0 24 23" fill="none">
                                <path d="M10.2679 2C11.0377 0.666667 12.9623 0.666667 13.7321 2L22.3923 17C23.1621 18.3333 22.1999 20 20.6603 20H3.33975C1.80015 20 0.837895 18.3333 1.6077 17L10.2679 2Z" stroke="#FF6725" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                <path d="M12 15C12.5523 15 13 15.4477 13 16C13 16.5523 12.5523 17 12 17C11.4477 17 11 16.5523 11 16C11 15.4477 11.4477 15 12 15ZM12 7C12.5523 7 13 7.44772 13 8V12C13 12.5523 12.5523 13 12 13C11.4477 13 11 12.5523 11 12V8C11 7.44772 11.4477 7 12 7Z" fill="#FF6725"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Scaling challenges across markets or regions</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exp-iss-col-btm">
                        <div class="exp-txt">
                            <p>Your brand breaks when you try to expand or internationalise.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .exp-lcol{
        width: 42%;
    }
    .exp-rcol{
        width: 56%;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .exp-iss-col{
        border-radius: 1.25rem;
        background: #252831;
        padding: 2rem;
        width: calc((100% - 1.5rem) / 2);
        height: 10.5rem;
    }
    .exp-iss-icon{
        margin-right: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: -0.3rem;
    }
    .exp-txt p{
        color: var(--white);
        font-family: 'pp_neue_montrealbook';
        font-size: 1em;
        line-height: 1.125rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.01rem;
        margin: 0;
    }
    .exp-iss-col-top {
        align-self: flex-start;
    }
    .exp-iss-col-top h3{
        min-height: 3rem;
    }
</style>